        void searchResults(java.util.ArrayList<CraftARResult> results,
                 long searchTimeMillis,
                 int requestCode)
        Callback with the results of an image recognition search.
        Parameters:
        results - List of matches for the given query,
        searchTimeMillis - Time to process this request.
        requestCode - Code passed to ImageRecognition.search(CraftARQueryImage,int) or -1 if no requestCode was passed.
